### ============================================================
### FacultyWare REST API — File Uji (pakai ekstensi "REST Client")
### ============================================================
###
### CARA PAKAI:
### 1. Install ekstensi VS Code: "REST Client" (oleh Huachao Mao)
### 2. Jalankan server: npm run dev
### 3. Klik tulisan "Send Request" yang muncul DI ATAS tiap request
### 4. WAJIB jalankan "0. LOGIN" dulu — cookie session disimpan otomatis
###
### Tip: response JSON muncul di panel sebelah kanan.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000


### ========== 0. LOGIN (JALANKAN INI DULU) ==========
# Akun lain: viewer@facultyware.com / password
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=admin@facultyware.com&password=password


### ========== STATISTIK ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats


### ========== KATEGORI: list semua ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/equipment-categories


### ========== KATEGORI: detail (id) ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/equipment-categories/1


### ========== KATEGORI: buat baru (POST) ==========
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/equipment-categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "KAT-01",
  "name": "Komputer",
  "description": "Peralatan komputer dan aksesoris"
}


### ========== KATEGORI: update (PUT) ==========
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/equipment-categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "KAT-01",
  "name": "Komputer (Diperbarui)",
  "description": "Deskripsi baru"
}


### ========== KATEGORI: hapus (DELETE) ==========
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/equipment-categories/1


### ========== ASET: list semua (+ search/filter) ==========
# Isi nilai setelah '=' untuk filter, atau biarkan kosong
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/equipments?q=&condition=&status=


### ========== ASET: detail (id) ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/equipments/1


### ========== ASET: buat baru (POST) ==========
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/equipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Dell XPS 13",
  "code": "IT-2026-001",
  "acquisition_type": "procurement",
  "acquisition_date": "2026-01-15",
  "acquisition_cost": 18500000,
  "condition": "good",
  "status": "available",
  "brand": "Dell",
  "model": "XPS 13 9310",
  "serial_number": "SN12345678",
  "specification": "Intel i7, RAM 16GB, SSD 512GB",
  "category_id": null
}


### ========== ASET: update (PUT) ==========
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/equipments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Dell XPS 13 (Update)",
  "code": "IT-2026-001",
  "acquisition_type": "procurement",
  "acquisition_date": "2026-01-15",
  "acquisition_cost": 18500000,
  "condition": "minor_damage",
  "status": "maintenance",
  "brand": "Dell",
  "model": "XPS 13 9310",
  "serial_number": "SN12345678",
  "specification": "Intel i7, RAM 16GB, SSD 512GB",
  "category_id": null
}


### ========== ASET: hapus (DELETE) ==========
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/equipments/1
